Joining #Tune4Tune campaign by @NFTune_ @metarupa_nft @hen_radio #hicetnunc #NFTcommunity #NFTaudio
The Music is from my personal project called Mesin Mesias, a solo audio project focused on making ambience - atmospheric - distinctive mood music.

The illustration is my reinterpretation for ancient creature norse mythology, called ' Fenrir ', aka Fenris Wolf (also given as Fenris-wolf) and Vanargand (“monster of van”) usually understood to mean “creature of expectation”.
